                  </did>
                  <altformavail>
                     <p>Microfilm copy available in <bibref title="https://www.thomasgray.org/resources/biblp.shtml#MeP_1991"
                                linktype="simple">
                           <title render="italic" linktype="simple">Poetic Commonplace Books and Manuscripts of Thomas Gray, 1716-1771, from Pembroke College, Cambridge</title> (1999),
								reel one</bibref>
                     </p>
                  </altformavail>
                  <bibliography>
                     <bibref title="https://www.thomasgray.org/resources/biblb.shtml#SmM_1989"
                             linktype="simple">Smith (ed.), <title render="italic" linktype="simple">Index</title> (1989), item GrT 136,  92</bibref>
                     <bibref title="https://www.thomasgray.org/resources/biblp.shtml#MeP_1999"
                             linktype="simple">
                        <title render="italic" linktype="simple">Poetic C.
								B.</title>, Pembroke College (1999),  30</bibref>
                  </bibliography>
                  <scopecontent>
                     <p>Transcript of ll. 1-2, 5-8, 3-4 in the hand of <extref href="https://www.thomasgray.org/resources/glnames.shtml#Mason, William, 1724-1797"
                                show="replace"
                                linktype="simple">
                           <persname normal="Mason, William,          1724-1797">William Mason</persname>
                        </extref>, here entitled <title render="doublequote" linktype="simple">Inscription on a portrait</title>, with ll. 3-4
								annotated "addition in the first Copy", in <persname normal="Gray, Thomas, 1716-1771" source="lcnaf">Gray</persname>'s <title render="italic" linktype="simple">Commonplace Book</title>, vol. III,  1106.
							</p>
